data.description: Price Reduced! North East end unit townhome with 3 bedrooms and 3 baths.  This home is located on a corner lot,  close to downtown of the waterfront town of North East with shops and restaurants and nearby access to Rt 40 and I95 for commuting. Located outside of town limits there is no HOA and no town taxes. This home is equipped with solar panels (leased) to lower electric billing. Amenities include a rear deck, faux fireplace, and enclosed front porch. Call now to tour!
